#- The birth of Trevieria§0
§0By: Trevie303§0
§0
§0Once upon a time, nikolazo imprisoned me for claiming my rightful land.§0
§0
§0That was a disgrace upon me§0
§0
§0And with all disgraces, there are virtues
#- And one particular virtue has came alive tonight§0
§0
