§0
§0The Trevierian nation and its followers§0
§0
§0And on this night, to the dismay of my enemies
#- I proclaim the nation of Trevieria!§0
§0
§0With me as King, and @callum as Queen§0
§0
§0And, to my hope, you are pleased
